=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F25%2F173716_4a681fc8fb6ebeed1591dcd54cfc288a.jpg&h=3fef1f37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n酒店係呢間</blockquote>"},{"pid":"2cb8a7054a720e8053b94a8bfc633d250fb0e7e8","tid":216571,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T09:44:33.000Z","msg":"有車牌就自駕遊<br />\n好方便仲好好玩<br />\n要去牛島行山，不過睇住時間行"},{"pid":"ab08f6202f7ce378a5879ee1a71d6f980ef723aa","tid":216571,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T09:48:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有車牌就自駕遊<br />\n好方便仲好好玩<br />\n要去牛島行山，不過睇住時間行</blockquote><br />\n冇車牌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n牛島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有其他景點/ 野食推介？"},{"pid":"226f7ffdd623e56dde2e8676ae81e66928e74c3a","tid":216571,"uid":49754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T10:21:30.000Z","msg":"如果自駕<br />\n住晒同一間酒店定分開好?"},{"pid":"cbb2501c7a63923ce9a5f21754bb98a7b93426a5","tid":216571,"uid":13837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:13:57.000Z","msg":"牛島景超靚 個人去行完係超開心超輕鬆"},{"pid":"410fcfdbff9e52ea2b463fde175f37148bd0c761","tid":216571,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:34:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果自駕<br />\n住晒同一間酒店定分開好?</blockquote><br />\n我冇車牌幫你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28cd37fbca158c08f34436e40cf7cdf6abec4b4a","tid":216571,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:34:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>牛島景超靚 個人去行完係超開心超輕鬆</blockquote><br />\n我會去 我間hotel近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ef35ab91823780dc43826ed007441d6040016c","tid":216571,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:36:03.000Z","msg":"暫時<br />\n<br />\n濟州民族村 牛島 龍頭岩 漢拏山 都會去<br />\n<br />\n有冇其他推介？"},{"pid":"03268e3a99ee86c51872721576184469a42d0822","tid":216571,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:36:42.000Z","msg":"仲有日出峰都會去"},{"pid":"1d7adcb72d8589d9fe53e91e073f1356fa5bc743","tid":216571,"uid":19891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:58:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>暫時<br />\n<br />\n濟州民族村 牛島 龍頭岩 漢拏山 都會去<br />\n<br />\n有冇其他推介？</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n民族村同龍頭岩都冇咩特別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可去可不去<br />\n<br />\n可以去中文旅遊區 同埋啲外島"},{"pid":"f277d467658d3900d225b716d65298f19dc939c6","tid":216571,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T12:55:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>濟州島6d6n<br />\nDay1<br />\n早上到達濟州機場&gt;附近早餐&gt;坐車到城山酒店&gt;myeongjin jeonbok&gt;酒店<br />\nDay2<br />\n附近沙灘&gt;日出峰&gt;aiya cafe&gt;酒店<br />\nDay3<br />\n漢拏山&gt;酒店<br />\nDay4<br />\n牛島(島上海鮮餐)&gt;酒店<br />\nDay5<br />\n坐車回濟州市中心&gt;check in 冠軍酒店&gt;市中心行&gt;donsadon&gt;酒店<br />\nDay6<br />\n東門市場&gt;龍頭岩&gt;橋村炸雞&gt;樂天汗蒸幕<br />\nDay7<br />\n早上回港<br />\n<br />\n其他:有時間就去<br />\n涉地可支,濟州民俗村<br />\n<br />\n巴絲有冇咩意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"453ff8860c16e3825bfd83e08633e144dfc152c4","tid":216571,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T12:56:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>暫時<br />\n<br />\n濟州民族村 牛島 龍頭岩 漢拏山 都會去<br />\n<br />\n有冇其他推介？</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n民族村同龍頭岩都冇咩特別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可去可不去<br />\n<br />\n可以去中文旅遊區 同埋啲外島</blockquote><br />\n原來係咁巴打對我個plan有咩意見？"},{"pid":"14119d73c5952ec29fda00c826eb53e3ef4db087","tid":216571,"uid":71462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:01:52.000Z","msg":"我都六月去濟州島<br />\n我book左濟洲市中心酒店<br />\n驚落雨無曬mood<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n交通方面好頭痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f468bbcc926997b35d395a0474b5a891dfa5be","tid":216571,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:05:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都六月去濟州島<br />\n我book左濟洲市中心酒店<br />\n驚落雨無曬mood<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n交通方面好頭痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打你個plan係點？<br />\n<br />\n我諗我會巴士 不過預先睇哂d巴士路線<br />\n<br />\n我諗加埋google map同app加問酒店同機場應該得"},{"pid":"4700d5c64d441e973292809d8283669c04f23a88","tid":216571,"uid":35097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:12:15.000Z","msg":"6 月一個去濟州自駕諗住環島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf799474942b0ed3097510bad6d6642c88b65621","tid":216571,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T11:29:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6 月一個去濟州自駕諗住環島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有車牌真好<br />\n<br />\n諗住去咩景點"},{"pid":"2b27bc6a8d7607954ad9dc317dcbd702d2f3958c","tid":216571,"uid":66104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T11:43:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都六月去濟州島<br />\n我book左濟洲市中心酒店<br />\n驚落雨無曬mood<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n交通方面好頭痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打你個plan係點？<br />\n<br />\n我諗我會巴士 不過預先睇哂d巴士路線<br />\n<br />\n我諗加埋google map同app加問酒店同機場應該得</blockquote><br />\n巴士有排等 班次又唔密 去得好少地方<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />伏過一次下次我再去一定租車或者自駕"},{"pid":"edd4d5b1ebc32b782cfde64bd567ad5968953629","tid":216571,"uid":35097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:38:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>6 月一個去濟州自駕諗住環島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有車牌真好<br />\n<br />\n諗住去咩景點</blockquote><br />\n未plan呀，但睇過d景點好散，咩區都有d咁<br />\n樓主主要去西歸蒲？唔知有冇機會撞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3664a182ff56468e3f6695ca27a1a4672c43b91e","tid":216571,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:25:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都六月去濟州島<br />\n我book左濟洲市中心酒店<br />\n驚落雨無曬mood<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n交通方面好頭痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打你個plan係點？<br />\n<br />\n我諗我會巴士 不過預先睇哂d巴士路線<br />\n<br />\n我諗加埋google map同app加問酒店同機場應該得</blockquote><br />\n巴士有排等 班次又唔密 去得好少地方<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />伏過一次下次我再去一定租車或者自駕</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 通常幾耐一班？"},{"pid":"f87e67cad8ca27109610681d11894b866b7cd5cb","tid":216571,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:26:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>6 月一個去濟州自駕諗住環島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有車牌真好<br />\n<br />\n諗住去咩景點</blockquote><br />\n未plan呀，但睇過d景點好散，咩區都有d咁<br />\n樓主主要去西歸蒲？唔知有冇機會撞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀 西歸蒲為主 同埋會去市中心"},{"pid":"629f3691be131fa823ce002cfbd5d395c97b49ee","tid":216571,"uid":13837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T16:29:10.000Z","msg":"去埋日出成峰 正呀喂 唔多記得叫咩正確名<br />\n一個唔行山既我（女）<br />\n邊行上山邊鬧 咁遠既<br />\n行到上山 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正呀"},{"pid":"d4f35d29b22e80332aa40bf55740176b1fbec84b","tid":216571,"uid":86260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T03:49:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去埋日出成峰 正呀喂 唔多記得叫咩正確名<br />\n一個唔行山既我（女）<br />\n邊行上山邊鬧 咁遠既<br />\n行到上山 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正呀</blockquote><br />\n城山日出峰？好多級樓梯<br />\nBtw 漢拏山要行足8，9個鐘"}]}